com.stephengware.java.ai.planning.ss

Class StateSpaceNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stephengware.java.ai.planning.ss.StateSpaceNode

  • public class StateSpaceNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a node in a state space search graph. A node is considered expanded once it is created. A node is considered visited once its expand() method has been called, at which point it expands all of its possible successor nodes (i.e. all possible next states).
    Author:
    Stephen G. Ware
